c: 3
v: 36
t: "So, as soon as she brought her forth, (i.e. gave birth to her) she said, \"Lord! Surely I have brought her forth, a female.\" And Allah knows best what she brought forth, and the male is not as the female. \"And surely I have named her Maryam. (Mary) And surely I take refuge with You for her and her offspring from the outcast Ash- shaytan.\" (The all vicious, i.e., the Devil)"